snippet.title: 2025 विश्वकर्मा पूजा आरती - Vishwakarma Aarti - Rinky Vishwakarma - Vishwakarma Pooja Aarti
snippet.description:
🙏 On the auspicious occasion of Vishwakarma Puja 2025, listen to the soulful Vishwakarma Aarti sung by Rinky Vishwakarma.
This divine aarti is dedicated to Lord Vishwakarma, the celestial architect and creator of the universe.

🌸 2025 विश्वकर्मा पूजा आरती | Vishwakarma Aarti | Rinky Vishwakarma 🌸

🙏 पावन अवसर पर प्रस्तुत है विश्वकर्मा पूजा 2025 की आरती, जिसे मधुर स्वर में गाया है रिंकी विश्वकर्मा ने।
यह दिव्य आरती भगवान विश्वकर्मा जी को समर्पित है, जिन्हें सृष्टि का दिव्य शिल्पकार और देवों के वास्तुकार माना जाता है।

👉 इस आरती को भक्तिभाव से सुनें और Like, Share & Subscribe करना न भूलें।

https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1363373145215357/

ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा प्रभु जय श्री विश्वकर्मा
सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

आदि सृष्टि में विधि को, श्रुति उपदेश दिया
शिल्प शस्त्र का जग में, ज्ञान विकास किया
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ऋषि अंगिरा ने तप से, शांति नही पाई
ध्यान किया जब प्रभु का, सकल सिद्धि आई
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

रोग ग्रस्त राजा ने, जब आश्रय लीना
संकट मोचन बनकर, दूर दुख कीना
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

जब रथकार दम्पती, तुमरी टेर करी
सुनकर दीन प्रार्थना, विपत्ति हरी सगरी
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

एकानन चतुरानन, पंचानन राजे
द्विभुज, चतुर्भुज, दशभुज, सकल रूप साजे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ध्यान धरे जब पद का, सकल सिद्धि आवे
मन दुविधा मिट जावे, अटल शांति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

श्री विश्वकर्मा जी की आरती, जो कोई नर गावे
कहत गजानन स्वामी, सुख सम्पत्ति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा प्रभु जय श्री विश्वकर्मा
सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma Prabhu Jai Shri Vishwakarma
Sakal Srishti Ke Karta Rakshak Shruti Dharma
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Aadi Srishti Mein Vidhi Ko, Shruti Updesh Diya
Shilp Shastra Ka Jag Mein, Gyaan Vikas Kiya
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rishi Angira Ne Tap Se, Shaanti Nahi Paayi
Dhyaan Kiya Jab Prabhu Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aayi
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rog Grast Raja Ne, Jab Aashray Leena
Sankat Mochan Bankar, Door Dukh Keena
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Jab Rathkaar Dampati, Tumri Ter Kari
Sunkar Deen Prarthana, Vipatti Hari Sagari
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Ekanan Chaturanand, Panchanan Raaje
DviBhuja, ChaturBhuja, Dashabhuja, Sakal Roop Saaje
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Dhyaan Dhare Jab Pad Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aave
Man Duvitha Mit Jaave, Atal Shaanti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Shri Vishwakarma Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Nar Gaave
Kahat Gajanan Swami, Sukh Sampatti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

This divine aarti is dedicated to Lord Vishwakarma, the celestial architect and creator of the universe.

🌸 2025 विश्वकर्मा पूजा आरती | Vishwakarma Aarti | Rinky Vishwakarma 🌸

🙏 पावन अवसर पर प्रस्तुत है विश्वकर्मा पूजा 2025 की आरती, जिसे मधुर स्वर में गाया है रिंकी विश्वकर्मा ने।
यह दिव्य आरती भगवान विश्वकर्मा जी को समर्पित है, जिन्हें सृष्टि का दिव्य शिल्पकार और देवों के वास्तुकार माना जाता है।

snippet.title: ANACONDA – Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
I like big snakes and I cannot lie. Paul Rudd and Jack Black star in #AnacondaMovie – exclusively in theatres Christmas.

Follow Us on Social:
https://x.com/Anaconda_Movie
https://www.facebook.com/AnacondaMovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@anacondamovie
https://www.instagram.com/anacondamovie

Visit our site: https://anacondamovie.com/

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Doug (Jack Black) and Griff (Paul Rudd) have been best friends since they were kids, and have always dreamed of remaking their all-time favorite movie: the cinematic "classic" Anaconda. When a midlife crisis pushes them to finally go for it, they head deep into the Amazon to start filming. But things get real when an actual giant anaconda appears, turning their comically chaotic movie set into a deadly situation. The movie they’re dying to make? It might just get them killed
 
Directed by:​​ 
Tom Gormican​
 
Written by:​​
Tom Gormican & Kevin Etten
​
Produced by: ​​​​
Brad Fuller
​​​​​Andrew Form
​​​​​Kevin Etten
​​​​​Tom Gormican
     
Executive Producer:​​​
Samson Mücke
 
Cast:​
Jack Black
​Paul Rudd
​Steve Zahn
​Thandiwe Newton
​Daniela Melchior
​Selton Mello
 
Credits not final

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, “Dude, same!” 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that’s funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you’re laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you’re caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it’s a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.


Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

Directed by S. J. Suryah | Produced by A. M. Rathnam – Sri Surya Movies | Music by Deva

snippet.description:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Because You r so perfect

Because You r so perfect

Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect

No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi

Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect

You r so perfect

You r so perfect

snippet.description:

#TheHousemaidMovie

THE HOUSEMAID is a wildly entertaining thriller starring Sydney Sweeney and Amanda Seyfried, based on the best-selling book. From director Paul Feig, the film plunges audiences into a twisted world where perfection is an illusion, and nothing is as it seems. Trying to escape her past, Millie (Sweeney) accepts a job as a live-in housemaid for the wealthy Nina (Seyfried) and Andrew Winchester (Brandon Sklenar). But what begins as a dream job quickly unravels into something far more dangerous – a sexy, seductive game of secrets, scandal, and power. Behind the Winchesters’ closed doors lies a world of shocking twists that will leave you guessing until the very end.

snippet.title: They Call Him OG | Release Trailer | Pawan Kalyan | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Entertainment
snippet.description:
They Call Him OG | Release Trailer | Pawan Kalyan | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Entertainment

The wait is finally over! Presenting the (Fan-Made) Release Trailer of They Call Him OG starring Power Star Pawan Kalyan in a mass action avatar. Directed by Sujeeth, with music by Thaman S, and produced by DVV Danayya under DVV Entertainment, this high-octane gangster action drama is all set to hit theatres on 25th September 2025.

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual.

Witness the ultimate action spectacle, breathtaking visuals, and Pawan Kalyan’s unstoppable screen presence that will set the box office on fire!

👉 Don’t miss the cinematic storm — #TheyCallHimOG is coming soon to rule theatres worldwide.

Release Date: 25th September 2025
Director: Sujeeth
Music: Thaman S
Banner: DVV Entertainment

#TheyCallHimOG #PawanKalyan #OGReleaseTrailer

Follow us on social media for the latest news:
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moviecruzzer/
- X handle: https://x.com/moviecruzzer

Visual fx, edit, Motion & Poster Design : Muhammad Naimur & Movie Cruzzer team.
Softwares used : Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects & Photoshop.

For business inquiries: moviecruzzerinfo@gmail.com

❯❯ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

We Follow All Youtube Term's

localized.title: They Call Him OG | Release Trailer | Pawan Kalyan | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Entertainment
localized.description:
They Call Him OG | Release Trailer | Pawan Kalyan | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Entertainment

The wait is finally over! Presenting the (Fan-Made) Release Trailer of They Call Him OG starring Power Star Pawan Kalyan in a mass action avatar. Directed by Sujeeth, with music by Thaman S, and produced by DVV Danayya under DVV Entertainment, this high-octane gangster action drama is all set to hit theatres on 25th September 2025.

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual.

Witness the ultimate action spectacle, breathtaking visuals, and Pawan Kalyan’s unstoppable screen presence that will set the box office on fire!

👉 Don’t miss the cinematic storm — #TheyCallHimOG is coming soon to rule theatres worldwide.

Release Date: 25th September 2025
Director: Sujeeth
Music: Thaman S
Banner: DVV Entertainment

#TheyCallHimOG #PawanKalyan #OGReleaseTrailer

Follow us on social media for the latest news:
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moviecruzzer/
- X handle: https://x.com/moviecruzzer

Visual fx, edit, Motion & Poster Design : Muhammad Naimur & Movie Cruzzer team.
Softwares used : Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects & Photoshop.

For business inquiries: moviecruzzerinfo@gmail.com

❯❯ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

snippet.title: एकादशी स्पेशल - वक्त खराब है तो अवश्य सुनें | KHATU SHYAM BHAJAN | EKADASHI BHAJAN 2025 | Gyaras
snippet.description:
एकादशी स्पेशल - वक्त खराब है तो अवश्य सुनें | KHATU SHYAM BHAJAN | EKADASHI BHAJAN 2025 | Gyaras

Songs: Khatuwala Jab Bhi Deta Deta Chappar Faad Ke + Teri Chaukhat Pe Aana Mera Kaam Hai + Wo Naseebo Se Jyada De Raha Hai + Lut Lo Nasibo Walo Ke Lut Bhayi Shyam Naam Ki + Jo Tum Nahi Doge Phir Kaun Dega Shyam + Dene Se Pehle Kya Kabhi Socha Hai Sanware + Thoda Deta Hai Ya Jyada Deta Hai 

⭐⭐⭐अपने दिन को बेहतर बनाने व् अपने श्याम बाबा के नए नए सुन्दर सुन्दर भजन रोज सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़े रहे || स्वस्थ रहें मस्त रहें  || जय श्री श्याम || जय श्री कृष्णा ||⭐⭐⭐

⭐ आज कल जगह जगह विडियो में बताये/ दिखाई देने वाले किसी भी उपाय पर विश्वास न करे
भजन के माध्यम से ही बाबा श्याम से प्राथना करके अपना जीवन सफल बनाए

snippet.title: DRX vs. NRG — VALORANT Champions Paris — Group Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ValorantEsports
Photos from the Event: https://www.flickr.com/photos/valorantesports/
Official VALORANT Esports News: https://valorantesports.com/news

snippet.title: Pujar Gaan (পূজার গান)| @HooliGaanism | Anirban, Subhadeep, Debraj, Gopinath | SVF Music | Puja 2025
snippet.description:
মাটির আখরে, মাটির সুরেই হোক মা দুগ্গার জয়গান 
শুনুন অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্য, শুভদীপ গুহ, দেবরাজ ভট্টাচার্য ও গোপীনাথ মুর্মুর সুরে, অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্য, শুভদীপ গুহ ও গোপীনাথ মুর্মুর লেখায়, অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্য, শুভদীপ গুহ আর দেবরাজ ভট্টাচার্যের কণ্ঠে Hooliganism-এর 'পূজার গান', শুধুমাত্র @SVFMusic  -এ। 

Let Maa Durga’s victory hymn be written in clay and sung in the tune of the earth 
Listen to Hooliganism’s ‘Pujar Gaan’, composed by Anirban Bhattacharya, Shubhadeep Guha, Debraj Bhattacharya, and Gopinath Murmu; written by Anirban Bhattacharya, Shubhadeep Guha, and Gopinath Murmu; and sung by Anirban Bhattacharya, Shubhadeep Guha, and Debraj Bhattacharya, only on @SVFMusic  .

#Hooligaanism #PujarGaan #SVFMusic

Presenting the new Haryanvi song 2025 – His Grace | Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra 

"His Grace" by Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra is a soulful Haryanvi track that blends emotions, powerful storytelling, and fresh melodies. With heartfelt lyrics and mesmerizing vocals, this song beautifully captures the essence of love, loyalty, and true emotions rooted in Haryana’s culture.

From deep emotions to unforgettable vibes, His Grace brings you a perfect balance of melody and meaning. If you love Haryanvi music with soul, this one is a must-listen!

Soulful Lyrics. Heart-touching Vibes. Pure Haryana Feels.

Song Credits:

Song Title: His Grace
Singer: Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra
Lyrics/Composer: Bintu Pabra
Additional Lyrics: Ndee Kundu
Music: Shine

Video By: Shubh Sandhu
Edit & Colourist: InkBlaze Studios

Producer: Dinesh Golan
Copyrights: Real Music & Ndee Kundu
Music Label: Ndee Kundu
Distribution Partner: EYP Creations & Warner Music India
Promotions Partner: Eyp Creations
Publicity Design & Digitally Managed By: Prince Pannu

#hisgrace #ndeekundu #bintupabra #newharyanvisong2025 #haryanvisong #haryanvimusic #haryanvilyrics #haryanvisinger #haryanvisong2025 #reelmusic #reelmusicharyana #haryanvitrending #trendingharyanvisong #haryanvilove #haryanvisoul

Lyrics:
Mne Jitna Kamaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maya Hai 
Manne Jo Bhi Kmaya Hai Uski Chattar Chaya Hai

Gaam K Main Chadra Bhaar Boot Cut Dekh 
Gaadi Hai Caror’an Aali Gaadi K Main Lath Dekh 
Hater Or Choriya Ne Bha Kit Khaan Deu 
Khaati Koniya Meri Bursat Silwat Dekh 
Dil K Naram Par Boli K Hain Tedhe Bore Balcony Main R Bhang Aale Peede
Maang Le Je Pyaar T To Jaan Bhi Ye Dede Beriyan Ki Chaatiyan Pe Maar Dyan Balede

Aajya Teri Taar Dyaa Takila Nakhro Chulhe Pe Hai Chaa Ka Patila Nakhro 
Bhittar Marod Konya Ek Pise Ki Vese To Carore Ka Hai Killa Nakhro 
Nyi Nyi Chiz Jo Sikhve Jma Daily Dahn Konya Deti Mere Dil Ki Hweli 
Positivity Ki Jine Kah Dyu Hu Dukan Main Suru Te Ae Meri Sun Eke Hai Saheli 

Yaariyan Main Noota Aala Hota Kde Jikra Ni Yaar Ki Hai Mehrbaani Yaara Pe Jo Likh Rya 
Haad Mne Tode Bhi Ghane Re Tudwaye Bhi Ghne 
Par Kise Main Bhi Jaan Mere Yaara Jisa Jigra Ni 

Hisse Jo Bhi Aaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maaya Hai 
Mne Jo Bhi Kamaya Hai Uki Chattarchya Hai 
Banda Bagwaan Ka Hu Kise Te Na Dru Main 
Thaare Aale Totkya Te Kde Koni Mru Main 
Khud Hi Kamana Mne Khud Hi Udaana 
Mkha Fer Kayate Parwa Re Duniya Ki Kru Main 

Baat Je Study Ki To Kri Mne Baarmi Baarmi K Baad Re Join Kra Army 
Mbd Ki Guide’an Te Sike Hoye Aan Royal Blood Makha Age Chale Tharvi 

Kuti Hoyi Mirch Hai R Micha Main Ghee Laasi Ki R Bhari Dhri Dekh Ketli 
Baajre Ki Roti Or Sarso Ka Saag Hai R Khaan K Main Yahe Hobby Tere Yaar Ki 

Udu Aasmaan Main Bhulya Konya Jad Meri 
Kadiya Bhi Fet Liyo Lage Konya Kad Meri 
Vo Khele Khaadya Me R Main Khelu Kalma Te 
Shillu Ki Jyu Sabda Pe Tej Hai Pakad Meri 
Maa Aale Haatha Jise Kite Bhi Swaad Ni 
Ghum Liye Duniya Re Ghar Jisi Baat Ni 
Mile Na Support Kite Bde Bhai Barga
Chache Jisa Yaar Nhi Babu Jisa Sath Nhi 

Gumaan Kre Kyaanka Main Ladla Hu Maa Ka 
Zameen’an Aale Yaar Jamidaar Nakhro Mhara To Pasina Mahange Bhaa Ka 
Ram Ki Jo Rja Hai Us Main Ae Raaji Haa
Bhoot Haare Baajiya R Bhoot Jite Baajiya 
Yaa Ae Sikhi Klla Mne Karya Bhoot Bhla Mne Loga Ki Jyu Kri Konya Kde Sosebaajiya

Hard Work Karya Hai R Dekhi Din Raat Nhi 
Dhoop Main Bhi Tape Haan R Ruke Barsaat Main Nhi 
Kaamyabi Gel Liye Ghin Ghin Badle 
Ora Ki Jyu Maari Kde Fokki Baat Baat Nhi 
Sath Mere Jitne Bhi Saare Chula Nyod Aale 
Ghar Te Bhi Bhaar Lage Gelya Khde Ghar Aale 
Kaam Bhaichaare Ke Karya Ye Ek Phone Main 
Khud Ne Dikha K Busy Kise Ke Na Kaam Tale 
Pad Jyagi Jhadjaygi Jitni Bhi Kaaya Hai 
Sath K Lejana Hai R Sath Main K Laaya Hai 
Ram Ka Vo Ghar Jime Aasn Bichya Hai 
Jitni Bhi Sampatti Hai Use Ka Kiraaya Hai 
Mne Jo Bhi Kamaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maaya Hai 
Re Jitni Bhi Maaya Hai Uki Chattarchaaya Hai

👥 Probable Playing XIs:

🇮🇳 India XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Suryakumar Yadav (C), Tilak Varma, Sanju Samson (wk), Shivam Dube, Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Kuldeep Yadav, Jasprit Bumrah, Varun Chakravarthy

🌤️ Pitch & Weather Report:

Pitch: Balanced wicket at Dubai, helpers for spin in middle overs; pacers get early rewards. 

average first-innings score here ~ 149. 

Weather: Clear skies expected, temperature high (~39.1°C IST), dry conditions. 


📝 Match Context / What to Watch:

India enters on strong form after a dominant win over UAE. Pakistan beat Oman convincingly. Both want vital Group A points. 

With Virat Kohli absent, India depend on Suryakumar Yadav, Shubman Gill, and the spin trio (Kuldeep, Varun Chakaravarthy, Axar) to control the middle overs. 

Pak’s batting threats: Mohammad Haris, Fakhar Zaman; their bowling led by Shaheen Afridi needs to strike early. 

Toss could be important — team batting first might get edge due to dew later in the innings.

snippet.title: Swathilo Muthyam Antha Full Video Song | Bangaru Bullodu Movie Songs | Balakrishna | Raveena Tandon
snippet.description:
Watch the superhit "Swathilo Muthyam Antha" full video song from the classic Telugu movie Bangaru Bullodu (1993) on @mangomusic. Starring the legendary Nandamuri Balakrishna, alongside gorgeous actresses Raveena Tandon and Ramya Krishna, this melodious song is a timeless hit. The beautiful lyrics by Veturi and soulful music by Raj-Koti make this a must-watch. Movie directed by Raviraja Pinisetty and  Produced by  V. B. Rajendra Prasad under the banner Jagapathi Art Pictures.

This evergreen song is a fan favorite for its catchy tune and mesmerizing visuals. Relive the golden era of Telugu cinema with this iconic 90s love song.

#SwathiloMuthyamanthaVideoSong #BangaruBulloduMovie #Balakrishna #raveenatandon #MangoMusic #ramyakrishnan #SPBalasubrahmaniyam #KSChitra #RajKoti #VeturiSundararamaMurthy #evergreenhitsongs #rainsongs #throwbackhits 

Song Details: 

Song Name: Swathilo Muthyamantha 
Singer: S. P. Balasubrahmaniyam,Chitra
Music : Raj-Koti
Lyricist: Veturi Sundararama Murthy 

Movie Details:

Movie Name: Bangaru Bullodu
Cast: Balakrishna, Raveena Tandon, Ramya Krishnan
Direction -  :  Raviraja Pinisetty
Produced by  V. B. Rajendra Prasad
Banner -  Jagapathi Art Pictures

Lyrics:

స్వాతిలో ముత్యమంత ముద్దులా ముట్టుకుంది సంధ్య వాన..
సందెలో చీకటంత సిగ్గులా అంటుకుంది లోనలోనా
అల్లో మల్లో...అందా....లెన్నో.. యాలో..ఓ..ఓ..యాల...
స్వాతిలో ముత్యమంత ముద్దులా ముట్టుకుంది సంధ్య వాన..
సందెలో చీకటంత సిగ్గులా అంటుకుంది లోనలోనా...

చరణం 1:

తాకిడి పెదవుల మీగడ తరకలు కరిగే వేళ..
మేనక మెరపులు.. ఊర్వశి ఉరుములు కలిసేనమ్మా..
కోకకు దరువులు రైకకు బిగువులు పెరిగే వేళ..ఆ..
శ్రావణ సరిగమ యవ్వన ఘుమఘుమ లయనీదమ్మ..
వానా వానా వల్లప్పా.. వాటేస్తేనే తప్పా..
సిగ్గు యెగ్గూ చెల్లెప్పా.. కాదయ్యో నీ గొప్పా..
నీలో...మేఘం.. నాలో దాహం.. యాలో.. యాల...
స్వాతిలో ముత్యమంత ముద్దులా ముట్టుకుంది సంధ్య వాన..
సందెలో చీకటంత సిగ్గులా అంటుకుంది లోనలోనా..

చరణం 2:
వానా వానా వచ్చేనంట.. వాగు వంకా మెచ్చేనంట..
తీగా డొంకా కదిలేనంట.. తట్టాబుట్టా కలిసేనంట..
ఎండా వానా పెళ్ళాడంగా.. కొండా కోనా నీళ్ళాడంగా..
 కృష్ణా గోదారమ్మ కలిసి.. పరవళ్ళెత్తి పరిగెత్తంగా
తుమ్మెద చురకలు తేనెల మరకలు కడిగే వాన
తిమ్మిరి నడుమున కొమ్మల తొడిమలు వణికే వాన..
జన్మకు దొరకని మన్మధ తలుపులు ముదిరే వాన..
చాలని గొడుగున నాలుగు అడుగుల నటనే వాన
వానల్లోన సంపెంగ.. ఒళ్ళంతా ఓ బెంగా..

Presenting the song, “Ayang Do:pid” from the movie #JIRJÍG 


🎵Credit:-
◾Film: Jirjíg
◾Song: Ayang Do:pid
◾Singer: Riyan Raj & Nisha Omé
◾Lyrics/Tune: Anand Doley & Gulap Bori
◾Music: Chandra kr. Patgiri 
◾ Mix & Master: Nilutpal Xobdo
◾ Producer: Nabam Arun Hina & Anku Bora


🎼Video Credits:
◾ Starring: Riyan Raj & Priyam Pallabee
◾ Cinematography | Editor | Colorist: Bhaskar Jyoti Doley
◾ Choreographer: Raju Rabha
◾ MUA: Vikash Rabha
◾ Asst MUA: Pompi Rabha

◾ Costume Designer: BhaskarBora
◾ Subtitle: Gulap Bori
◾ GFX: Pranjeet Doley


🎬 Movie Credits:
◾ Movie: Jirjíg 
◾ Script: Danny Doley
◾ Director: Danny Doley, Bhaskar Jyoti Doley 
◾ Producer: Nabam Arun Hina | Anku Bora 
◾ D.O.P | Editor | Colorist | Action Director: Bhaskar Jyoti Doley
◾ GFX : Pranjeet Doley
◾ Music & Background Score: Nilutpal Xobdo  (Xobdo Studio)
◾ MUA: Vikash Rabha
◾ Production Designer: Riyan Raj 
◾ Subtitle: Srishti Rani Taid
◾ GFX: Pranjeet Doley

 ✍️Lyrics:

   Nom aipé mé:namsém lusarsupé
Gompiré pí:ramdag
Nom asin onamsém léngkanpé
Adísé pí:ramdag

Ka:tí:sunamko
Ka:la du:pé (nom)
Kéra:so bogabge:l
A:pén longédo:p
Gíjonsula:pé
Alagdok sogabge:l

No mukkangé
Ngo do:míré
No ésaré
Ngo pédongé
     
Ngonyik ayang do:piddo jardag
 Ayang amíngé

1.
Adjouné agomdokké
Arainé do:yingé lendung
Mé:bonamdé:sin silo mé:nampé idung

Ma:nyíngé kinsula
Alab labla dé:dung
Asinang onamdé aya:pé idung


2.
Arop aipé mé:nédé
Agomém lukursumang
Angkéng/Asin pogla du:namém
Ammem tadmomang

Rongngamko ara:do:sin
Nok gomugém tatpa:dag
Mikjémna du:dodo:sin
Nommíng ka:pa:dag
